OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly dry start, perhaps brief
OL,6,Fbrighter spells, before cloud soon
OL,7,Fthickens from the west. Rain moving
OL,8,Finto western parts through the
OL,9,Fafternoon, turning persistent and
OL,10,Fheavy at times, with some outbreaks
OL,11,Falso spreading further east. Breezy,
OL,12,Fespecially over the Pennines.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FRain or drizzle clearing most
OL,15,Fparts by midnight, although the odd
OL,16,Fspot of drizzle perhaps continuing in
OL,17,Fthe far south. Staying rather cloudy,
OL,18,Fwith hill fog. Winds becoming light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
