OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FCloudy, but mostly dry,
OL,6,Falthough outbreaks of light rain or
OL,7,Fdrizzle remains possible. These most
OL,8,Flikely across Humberside or with any
OL,9,Fhill fog, and most likely through the
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,13,Fwith rain Saturday morning, clearing
OL,14,Fto brighter spells later, and
OL,15,Fovernight frost. Winds strengthening
OL,16,FSunday and Monday, with some rain
OL,17,Fspreading east, but also drier and
OL,18,Fbrighter intervals. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
